<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="highly-adv">highly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'haɪli/    美 /'haɪli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>很；非常；高度地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>highly successful / effective / efficient / important 
非常成功的/有效的/有效率的/重要的</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a highly paid job
高薪的工作</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>think / speak highly of</strong>
对…高度评价</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Food safety is <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (high) important, so the government spares no effort to prevent food pollution.  （2008 上海改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. highly  </p></div>